Create Both
Expunge Both
SyncState *

# ------Gmail Personal------
IMAPAccount Gmail_Personal
Host imap.gmail.com
Port 993
User bm.silva.oliveira@gmail.com
PassCmd "pass show Gmail/Personal_Mutt"
SSLType IMAPS
CertificateFile /etc/ssl/certs/ca-certificates.crt

IMAPStore Gmail_Personal-remote
Account Gmail_Personal

MaildirStore Gmail_Personal-local
Path ~/.local/share/Mail/Gmail_Personal/
Inbox ~/.local/share/Mail/Gmail_Personal/INBOX
Subfolders Verbatim

Channel Gmail_Personal-inbox
Master :Gmail_Personal-remote:
Slave :Gmail_Personal-local:
Patterns * # Include everything
#Patterns * ![Gmail]* "[Gmail]/Sent Mail" "[Gmail]/Starred" "[Gmail]/All Mail" # Include everything but

